                            <p><pre></pre><strong>Please Note: </strong>In case of special train journey (like Palace on Wheels, Royal Rajasthan on Wheels, Deccan Odyssey, Golden Chariot, Indian Maharaja &amp; Maharajas Express) – a separate cancellation policy is applicable (which would be advised as and when required).
